4/19

Bas16 colour schemes
Set manually as needed.  Don't set in .zshrc

    Dark
    base16_harmonic-dark - dark blue bg
    base16_material - dark grey/green
    base16_hopscotch  - brown/red

    Light
    base16_gruvbox-light-soft

Base16 config
    Vim - Vungle plugin


